00:01:41.956 --> 00:01:44.510
seeing the world accurately?

00:01:44.510 --> 00:01:45.259
Sorry.

00:01:45.259 --> 00:01:46.550
AUDIENCE: You're gonna tell us.

00:01:46.550 --> 00:01:47.390
BEAU LOTTO: I'm
