00:01:47.390 --> 00:01:47.889
So--

00:01:47.889 --> 00:01:48.970
[LAUGHTER]

00:01:48.970 --> 00:01:49.480
--I think--

00:01:49.480 --> 00:01:50.685
[LAUGH]

00:01:50.685 --> 00:01:51.520
--but I'm curious.

00:01:51.520 --> 00:01:54.680
