00:11:44.840 --> 00:11:48.546
how to put an H between that
W and A. Why do you do so?

00:11:48.546 --> 00:11:50.420
Because your brain has
encoded the statistics

00:11:50.420 --> 00:11:53.310
of co-ocurring letters in the
English and other languages.

00:11:53.310 --> 00:11:56.900
So when you're presented with
a completely arbitrary context

00:11:56.900 --> 00:11:58.640
of W space AT, you
put an H there,

00:11:58.640 --> 00:12:01.580
because it was useful
to do so in the past.

00:12:01.580 --> 00:12:04.367
But there's no inherent
value in this letter string.

00:12:04.367 --> 00:12:05.450
It's completely arbitrary.

00:12:05.450 --> 00:12:08.210
It doesn't exist without us.

00:12:08.210 --> 00:12:11.660
And also notice, none of you
read, what are you dreaming?

00:12:11.660 --> 00:12:13.480
Because I had you reading.

