That was your recent history.

00:12:15.000 --> 00:12:18.570
So you interpreted this in
terms of your recent history.

00:12:18.570 --> 00:12:21.050
So you read, what are
you reading, right?

00:12:21.050 --> 00:12:24.090
And this is true at the most
basic level of perception.

00:12:24.090 --> 00:12:25.820
So if you think
back to lightness,

00:12:25.820 --> 00:12:27.980
which again, is our
simplest perception,

00:12:27.980 --> 00:12:30.980
you'll see a dark brown tile at
the top and a light orange tile

00:12:30.980 --> 00:12:32.480
at the side, yes?

00:12:32.480 --> 00:12:34.636
That is your
perception of reality.

00:12:34.636 --> 00:12:38.570
You will bet your life that
they are different, yes?

00:12:38.570 --> 00:12:42.520
When in fact, they're
exactly the same.

00:12:42.520 --> 00:12:43.990
Nothing is changing
on the screen

00:12:43.990 --> 00:12:47.860
at all except the
meaning of the data.

00:12:47.860 --> 00:12:49.404
You're seeing not
the information,

00:12:49.404 --> 00:12:50.820
but the meaning
of the information

00:12:50.820 --> 00:12:51.880
based on your history.

00:12:51.880 --> 00:12:53.860
And not just your history.

00:12:53.860 --> 00:12:56.050
The history of your
culture and the history

00:12:56.050 --> 00:12:58.600
of your evolutionary ancestors.

00:12:58.600 --> 00:13:02.110
Most of your life happened
without you there.

00:13:02.110 --> 00:13:06.547
We come into the world with all
kinds of perceptual meanings.

00:13:06.547 --> 00:13:08.380
What's true for color
is also true for form.

00:13:08.380 --> 00:13:13.520
So these two tables
are the same, agreed?

00:13:13.520 --> 00:13:14.020
No?

00:13:14.020 --> 00:13:15.770
[LAUGHTER]

