00:21:56.990 --> 00:21:58.990
I mean we're literally
like this frog.

00:21:58.990 --> 00:22:01.930
So this is virtual
reality for a frog, right?

00:22:04.510 --> 00:22:05.010
Right?

00:22:05.010 --> 00:22:06.572
It's getting a
stimulus, and it's

00:22:06.572 --> 00:22:08.780
generating behavior that
was useful in the past, just

00:22:08.780 --> 00:22:09.380
like us.

00:22:12.850 --> 00:22:15.302
It's like a "Black Mirror"
